          tree; and all elements integrated into the screen interfaces and the navigation
          tree (hereinafter, the Content) and all those online services or resources that
          may be offered to Users (hereinafter, the Services).
        </p>
        <p>
          <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> reserves the right to modify, at any
          time and without prior notice, the presentation and configuration of the Website
          and the Content and Services that may be incorporated therein. The User acknowledges
          and accepts that <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> may interrupt, deactivate,
          and/or cancel any of these elements that are integrated into the Website or access
          to them at any time.
        </p>
        <p>
          The access to the Website by the User is free and generally does not require a
          subscription or registration. The User shall bear the cost of connection through
          the telecommunications network provided by the access provider contracted by the
          User.
        </p>
        <p>
          The use of any of the Content or Services of the Website may be made through the
          subscription or prior registration of the User.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="user">
        <h3>The User</h3>
        <p>
          The access, browsing, and use of the Website, as well as the spaces enabled for
          interaction among Users, and the User and
          <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} />, such as comments and/or blogging
          spaces, confer the status of User, for which all the Terms established here are
          accepted from the moment the Website is accessed, without prejudice to the
          application of the corresponding mandatory legal regulations as appropriate.
          Given the relevance of the foregoing, the User is recommended to read them each
          time they visit the Website.
        </p>
        <p>
          The Website of <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> provides a great diversity
          of information, services, and data. The User assumes responsibility for making proper
          use of the Website. This responsibility shall extend to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <p>
              The use of the information, Content, and/or Services and data offered by
              <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> without contravening the provisions
              of these Terms, the Law, morality, or public order, or that in any other way
              may cause injury to the rights of third parties or the same operation of the
              Website.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              The veracity and legality of the information provided by the User in the
              forms issued by <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> for access to
