              misuse of the information registered in such forms, such as, but not limited
              to, theft, loss, or unauthorized access to identifiers and/or passwords, in order
              to proceed to their immediate cancellation.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> reserves the right to withdraw all
          comments and contributions that violate the law, the respect for the dignity of the
          person, that are discriminatory, xenophobic, racist, pornographic, spam, that threaten
          youth or childhood, public order or security, or that, in its opinion, are not suitable
