        from which it is made, nor the knowledge and acceptance of
        <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} /> of the content, services, and/or activities
        offered on that website, and vice versa.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="intellectual-industrial-property">
      <h2>Intellectual and Industrial Property</h2>
      <p>
        <span translate="no" set:text={companyName} />, by itself or as an assignee, is
        the owner of all intellectual and industrial property rights of the Website, as
        well as the elements contained therein (by way of example, but not limited to,
